            "title": "盤中速報 - 雙鴻(3324)股價拉至漲停，漲停價1215.0元，成交7,529張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雙鴻(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3324-TW</a>)24日11:18上漲110元，股價漲停報1215.0元，委買62,000張、委賣826,000張，成交7,529張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為散熱模組。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雙鴻(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3324-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲5.74%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲4.2%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,292 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,626 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+58 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-392 張</li> <li>融資增減：-458 張</li> <li>融券增減：+53 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
